Over 200,000 people live there. Founded in 1903. It is at the western edge of the fertile Oxnard Plain, and is one of the world's most important agricultural places, that has the strawberry and lima bean capital. ==References== == Other websites == * City of Oxnard website * Oxnard @ The Official Conejo Valley Website, a website with local history, events, and community information.
